HEADWORD: Autotheism
<hw>Au"to*the`ism</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Auto-</ets> + theism.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The doctrine of
God's self-existence.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Deification of one's self; self-worship.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Autotheist</ent>⟦br⟧
